        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to them a God; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "so that if God had not designed this, he would have been ashamed ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to be called their God, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Hebrews 11:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". As the land of Canaan was secured to the seed of Abraham, according to the flesh; so heaven is secured to all his spiritual seed for a possession truly everlasting. The offer of this eternal life is made in the word, and the earnest of it is given to all believers.",
        "children": []
